README for sensor_test

This application is used to demonstrate functioning drivers & hardware.
It usses the commander daemon, so a mos_terminal must be loaded on the
host. (execute mantis.elf in the mantis/build/linux/src/apps/commander 
directory).

commands:
help - (prints this list)
leds - asks for a number and displays it in binary (only accepts 1-7)
get temp - sample the current temperature and convert it to degrees F
get light - get the percentage light in the room
sounder on - turn on the sounder
sounder off - turn off the sounder ** DOESN'T WORK **